en_question:
    Jinyuan Company produces three types of products over a planning period divided into three stages. A production plan needs to be formulated to determine the quantity of each product to be produced at each stage.
 The plan is constrained by market demand, equipment working hours, and financial capital. Relevant data are shown in Table 4-16 and Table 4-17. It is assumed that the initial and final inventories of all products are zero. 

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Table 4-16: Product Demand at Each Stage}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccc}
        \toprule
        Demand Stage & Product 1 & Product 2 & Product 3 \\
        \midrule
        1 & 500 & 750 & 900 \\
        2 & 680 & 800 & 800 \\
        3 & 800 & 950 & 1000 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{Table 4-17: Resource Consumption per Unit Product and Stage Resource Limits}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccc|c}
        \toprule
        Item & Product 1 & Product 2 & Product 3 & Stage Resource Limit \\
        \midrule
        Equipment Working Hours (h) & 2.0 & 1.0 & 3.1 & 5000 \\
        Working Capital Occupied (yuan) & 40 & 20 & 55 & 93000 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

The company sets the following three prioritized objectives: 1.Timely delivery to meet demand, minimizing stockouts. The importance of timely delivery for Product 3 is twice that of Products 1 and 2. 2.Minimize overloading of processing equipment at each stage. 3.Ensure that working capital usage does not exceed the limit.Please formulate a mathematical model and optimize it accordingly.

cn_question:
    金源公司生产三种产品，整个计划期分为三个阶段。现需编制生产计划，确定各个阶段各种产品的生产数量。

计划受市场需求、设备台时、财务资金等方面条件的约束，有关数据如表 4-16 和表 4-17 所示。假设计划期初及期末各种产品的库存量皆为零。

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{各阶段产品需求量（表 4-16）}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccc}
        \toprule
        需求阶段 & 产品 1 & 产品 2 & 产品 3 \\
        \midrule
        1 & 500 & 750 & 900 \\
        2 & 680 & 800 & 800 \\
        3 & 800 & 950 & 1000 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

\begin{table}[h]
    \centering
    \caption{每台产品资源消耗量及阶段资源限制（表 4-17）}
    \renewcommand{\arraystretch}{1.2}
    \begin{tabular}{c|ccc|c}
        \toprule
        项目 & 产品 1 & 产品 2 & 产品 3 & 每阶段资源限制 \\
        \midrule
        设备工作台时/h & 2.0 & 1.0 & 3.1 & 5000 \\
        流动资金占用量/元 & 40 & 20 & 55 & 93000 \\
        \bottomrule
    \end{tabular}
\end{table}

公司设定以下三个优先级的目标：
\begin{enumerate}
    \item $P_1$：及时供货，保证需求，尽量减少缺货，并且第三种产品及时供货的重要性相当于第一种、第二种产品的 2 倍；
    \item $P_2$：尽量使各阶段加工设备不超负荷；
    \item $P_3$：流动资金占用量不超过限额；
\end{enumerate}
请建立其数学模型并优化
